name: Rozalin - Disgaea 5
description:
From a request, I decided to make Rozalin from Disgaea 2... And also because the Disgaea franchise is just super underrated, as are all the characters from it. It was trained on animefull_final with 18 (I wish there was more high quality images of her :( ). images with the usual self-pruning and tagging and a wide range of different images. I like keeping my prompts simple for the first few pictures so that you can see it without a whole bunch of mumbo jumbo. Make your pictures better than mine though!

What does it do you ask? Rozalin in her base outfit.

How to use it: Simple for this LORA as well. Just the trigger word of:

RozalinD2 - Main trigger word.

Otherwise, add whatever you want it to lean towards. Or if you want different outfits.

Extra, Extra!: Should be well trained and usable in most models. Images shown for example.

Picture Descriptions:

1-2: AnythingV3 using just this Lora.

3: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Knight-ify Locon.

4: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Dominatrix Locon.

5: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Jiangshi Transformation Locon.

6: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Symbiote Taking Over Locon.

7: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Brainwashing Machine Locon.

8: AnythingV3 combo'd with my in progress Defaultz17 style Locon.

9: AbyssOrange with just this Lora.

10: PerfectWorld using just this Lora.

11: ChilloutMix using just this Lora.

What's next for this? I think this should be good, unless feedback goes shows me making a mistake somewhere.

What's next that isn't this?

More character Loras. (Ivy from Soul Calibur 5, Heine from Combatants Will Be Dispatched, Conqueror Lilias from E7, Evelynn from LoL (both base and All Out version), Tharja from Fire Emblem, Catherine from Catherine Full Body, Miku from Idaten Deities, Kuribayashi Shino from GATE, Rin Sohma from Fruits Basket, Kasumi from P5, Ann from P5, Ikumi Mito from Food Wars, Alice Nakiri from Food Wars, Chika Fujiwara from Kaguya-sama, Lulu from FF10, Momo from My Hero, Vivy from Vivy, Lucoa and Tohru from Dragon Maid, Dominique de Sade from Vanitas, and Dos from One Punch Man.) And maybe Wilhelm van Astrea, my favorite Re:Zero husbando or a Prinny from Disgaea.

V2's of some of the previous Loras. Specifically make them more diversely acceptable with other models and LORA's.

I also have some more quite NSFW Locon's. I decided to list them as well, so if people have preferences on which to fix up first let me know. Specifically, Symbiote Taking Over (imagine a venom-like symbiote taking over your waifu), being stepped on, Robotification, Petrified (I'm unsure if I should bother with this one anymore), Infection (this one is VERY nsfw, as the waifu is completely infected), Dominatrix (waifu becoming a dominatrix), Brainwashing Machine, Tentacles, Pillory, Masked Evil (A mask that possess' the waifu), Latex Corruption, Combat Drone (hard to describe but basically making them a mindless sci-fi combat warrior), JAV Supervillain, Jiangshi (Transforms into a Jiangshi), Mind Flayer Defeat, Harem Outfits, Hourglass Figure (just to make your waifu curvy), and Holding a Leash.

And, uh, I want to make a few "normal" Locon's so I have an "knight-ify" your character one coming up. And a forest fairy one as well. And a officer one. And a barbarian one.

Additionally, I love the style of Defaultz_17, so I'm making a Locon to mirror that.

Or just give me some random suggestion or priority opinions. That works too.
